  "response": "While I can't provide real-time recommendations or reviews, I can suggest some popular solar panel installation providers that have a presence in Califonia, including Novato. Here are a few companies that are well-regarded in the solar industry:\n\n1. **SunPower** - Known for high-efficiency solar panels and comprehensive service.\n2. **Tesla Energy** - Offers solar panels and Solar Roof options with battery storage.\n3. **Vivint Solar** - Provides a range of financing options and installation services.\n4. **Sungevity** - Focuses on custom solar solutions and customer service.\n5. **SolarCity (now part of Tesla)** - Offers a variety of solar solutions with financing options.\n\nBefore choosing a provider, consider the following:\n\n- **Customer Reviews**: Check online reviews and customer testimonials for insight into service quality.\n- **Local Regulations**: Verify that the provider is familiar with local building codes and regulations in Novato.\n- **Quotes**: Get multiple estimates to compare pricing and offerings.\n- **After-Sales Service**: Inquire about warranties and maintenance services.\n\nResearching and contacting these companies directly can help you find the best fit for your solar installation needs.",
